Add Vector Layer
→ Go to Layer → Add Layer → Add Vector Layer
→ Select GIS_Workshop\Manual\Prac06\IND_adm0.shp

Enable Georeferencer Plugin
→ Go to Plugins → Manage and Install Plugins
→ Install/Ensure Georeferencer GDAL is enabled.

Open Georeferencer
→ Go to Raster → Georeferencer
→ File → Open Raster
→ Select 1870_southern-india_3975_3071_600.jpg

Transformation Settings
→ Settings → Transformation Settings

Transformation Type: Thin Plate Spline
Resampling: Nearest Neighbour
CRS: Everest 1830 datum (EPSG 4044)
Output Raster: Choose file name & location
Check Load in QGIS when done
→ Press OK
Add Control Points
→ Edit → Add Points (select GCPs on raster and reference layer)

Run Georeferencing
→ Settings → Transformation Settings → RUN
→ Then File → Start Georeferencing
